title: Island of Stars and Chains
description: Island of Stars and Chains Manhwa Gi Seunghyun always dreamed of becoming a Hunter, but he is plagued by despair due to his lack of ability. Then one day, his older sister, Gi Sohyun, awakens from a 12-year coma. Just as they begin to reunite, the siblings find themselves caught in an unfathomable, shocking event. 별과 사슬이 뜨는 섬, The Island Of Rising Stars And Chains
alternative_titles: The Island Of Rising Stars And Chains
